  "description": "<p>分类: <a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/category/gaming/\" rel=\"tag\">游戏产品</a></p><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"cn.engadget.com/2013/07/09/deus-ex-the-fall-july-11/\"><img src=\"http://www.blogcdn.com/cn.engadget.com/media/2013/07/deusexthefall.jpg\" style=\"margin: 4px;\" /></a></div>\n\n<div><br />\n早前 Square Enix 公司<a href=\"http://Deus Ex: The Fall is sneaking / punching / stalking its way to iOS on July 11th, Square Enix announced this morning. When it arrives, it'll cost you nearly a sawbuck ($6.99 / £4.99 / 5.99€), and work on a wide variety of iOS devices (iPad 2 and above, iPhone 4S and above, and iPod Touch 5 and above). But which way will you play it? Us, well, we're all about refrigerator stacking.\">宣布</a>他们的「Deus Ex: The Fall」游戏将在这个夏季里登陆手机和平板设备，现在他们有进一步的宣布了。毫不意外地，他们将会先在 7 月 11 号把这款游戏带到 iOS 的装置中，支持 iPad 2 或以上、iPhone 4S 或以上以及第五代 iPod touch 或以上，而价钱方面则是 US$6.99（约 43 元人民币）。这款游戏的背景是 2027 年，集动作和射击于一身，如果大家有兴趣了解的话，可以到继续阅读看看介绍影片。</div><p><br /><p class=\"continueReading\"><a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2013/07/09/deus-ex-the-fall-july-11/\" rel=\"bookmark\">继续阅读全文 <em>Deus Ex: The Fall 游戏将在 7 月 11 号登陆 iOS（视频）</em></a></p><h6 style=\"clear: both; padding: 8px 0 0 0; height: 2px; font-size: 1px; border: 0; margin: 0; padding: 0;\"></h6><a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2013/07/09/deus-ex-the-fall-july-11/\" rel=\"bookmark\" title=\"Permanent link to this entry\">此文章网址</a>&nbsp;|&nbsp;<a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/forward/20651556/\" title=\"Send this entry to a friend via email\">转寄此文章</a>&nbsp;|&nbsp;<a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2013/07/09/deus-ex-the-fall-july-11/#comments\" title=\"View reader comments on this entry\">回应</a><hr size=\"1\" />", 
